# ReFrame environment variables. Copy to `.env.local` and fill in as needed.

# --- LLM (copy rewriting) ---------------------------------------------------
# Without a key, generation falls back to deterministic, non-AI copy.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
# Optional model override (defaults to a sensible current model).
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=

# --- Published-site storage -------------------------------------------------
# Default: file-backed store under .data/ (good for local + single instance).
# Override the data dir if you like:
# REFRAME_DATA_DIR=.data/sites
#
# For serverless / multi-instance, attach a Vercel KV (or Upstash Redis) store.
# When BOTH of these are set, publishing (and user accounts) automatically use
# KV instead of disk - no code change required.
# KV_REST_API_URL=
# KV_REST_API_TOKEN=

# --- Accounts / sessions ----------------------------------------------------
# Secret used to sign session cookies. Set a long random value in production
# (e.g. `openssl rand -hex 32`). A dev fallback is used when unset.
# AUTH_SECRET=

# --- Billing (Stripe) -------------------------------------------------------
# Billing activates only when the secret key, webhook secret and at least the
# Pro price are set. Until then, checkout/portal return a clear "not configured"
# response and the app runs unchanged.
# STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_...
# STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_...        # from `stripe listen` or the dashboard
# STRIPE_PRICE_PRO=price_...             # recurring price for Pro
# STRIPE_PRICE_STUDIO=price_...          # recurring price for Studio
